subject: Wimbledon Tennis Tournament
Tennis
Suspensions, Dismissals and Resignations
lead_paragraph: The 1997 champion, ninth-seeded Martina Hingis, fought off two match points before beating Naomi Cavaday, an 18-year-old from England ranked 232nd in the world.
